 <text id="F0637T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Bloss writes his sister about their brother William's illness and how it is impossible for
     him to visit or bring his brother home.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">His Sister</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1864-08-06">Aug. 6<hi rend="super">th</hi>. 1864</date>
      <name type="place">Washington City, D.C.</name>
     </dateline>
     <salute>Dear Sister,</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>I received yours of the 4<hi rend="super">th</hi>
     <orig reg="today">to day</orig>. I am <orig reg="sorry">sory</orig> to tell you that I <orig
      reg="can't">cant</orig> go to see William. we <orig reg="arrived">arived</orig> here last
     night in Washington. and we are going <orig reg="today">to day</orig> to Maryland to drive the
     invading rebels from the <orig reg="borders">boaders</orig> of Pennsylvania. I expect we will
     have a fight with them tomorrow. I am about two hundred and sixty miles from William now. and I
      <orig reg="can't">cant</orig> go to see him on any account that I can fix it. we <orig
      reg="were">where</orig> three days on the water coming here with our horses on board. I <orig
      reg="can't">cant</orig> do anything for William whatever, so you will have to do the best that
     you can to have him home, take what money I have home and do the best with it you can in having
     him home &amp; if it <orig reg="don't">dont</orig> reach<pb n="2"/>
     <orig reg="borrow">borow</orig> money and I will Pay all <orig reg="expenses">expencess</orig>.
     I have six <orig reg="months">month</orig> Pay coming to me now and I expect to get <orig
      reg="paid">Pay</orig> in a few days or two weeks.</p>

    <p>I am well and in good health hoping that this will find you the same.</p>

    <closer>
     <salute>from your Brother</salute>
     <signed>J. Bloss</signed>
     <seg type="postscript">my address - Co. K. 17<hi rend="super">th</hi>. Pa. Cavalry<lb/> 2<hi
       rend="super">nd</hi>. Brig. 1<hi rend="super">st</hi>. Cav. Div.<lb/> Washington, D.C.</seg>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
 </text>
